### Search Service — HTTP Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8085
### Start service: pnpm nx serve search-service (requires Docker infra: elasticsearch + rabbitmq)
### All search endpoints are public (no auth required)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8085

# A real artistId from catalog-service (fill in after indexing)
@artistId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UNIFIED SEARCH — GET /api/v1/search
# Returns both tracks and artists in one response
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [1] Search all — basic query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=love

###

### [2] Search all — with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=rock&page=0&size=10

###

### [3] Search all — page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=pop&page=1&size=5

###

### [4] Search all — empty query (returns latest/all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=

###

### [5] Search all — size exceeds max (100) → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=test&size=200

###

### [6] Search all — negative page → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=test&page=-1

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TRACK SEARCH — GET /api/v1/search/tracks
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [7] Search tracks — basic query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=love

###

### [8] Search tracks — sort by relevance (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=chill&sort=relevance

###

### [9] Search tracks — sort by newest
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=chill&sort=newest

###

### [10] Search tracks — sort by most popular
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=chill&sort=popular

###

### [11] Search tracks — filter by genre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=love&genre=POP

###

### [12] Search tracks — filter by artistId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=&artistId={{artistId}}

###

### [13] Search tracks — genre + artistId + sort combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=love&genre=BALLAD&artistId={{artistId}}&sort=popular&page=0&size=10

###

### [14] Search tracks — Vietnamese query (Unicode)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=yêu

###

### [15] Search tracks — fuzzy match (typo in query)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=muisc

###

### [16] Search tracks — invalid sort value → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=test&sort=unknown

###

### [17] Search tracks — size too large → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=test&size=999

###

### [18] Search tracks — query that returns no results → 200 empty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/tracks?q=zzzzzzz_no_results_xyzabc

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ARTIST SEARCH — GET /api/v1/search/artists
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [19] Search artists — basic query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=son

###

### [20] Search artists — with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=nguyen&page=0&size=10

###

### [21] Search artists — empty query (returns all artists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=

###

### [22] Search artists — Vietnamese query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=sơn

###

### [23] Search artists — query that returns no results → 200 empty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=zzzzzzz_no_results_xyzabc

###

### [24] Search artists — size too large → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/artists?q=test&size=999

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTOCOMPLETE — GET /api/v1/search/autocomplete
# Returns mixed track + artist suggestions sorted by text
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [25] Autocomplete — short prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=lo

###

### [26] Autocomplete — 3-char prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=lov

###

### [27] Autocomplete — custom limit (max 10 results)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=lo&limit=10

###

### [28] Autocomplete — limit=1 (minimum)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=lo&limit=1

###

### [29] Autocomplete — limit exceeds max (20) → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=lo&limit=50

###

### [30] Autocomplete — Vietnamese prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=yê

###

### [31] Autocomplete — prefix with no matches → 200 empty suggestions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search/autocomplete?q=zzz

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH & METRICS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [32] Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### [33] Prometheus metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics
Accept: text/plain

###
